{{Infobox Basketball club | name = Blauw-Wit | logo = | imagesize = | leagues = [[Korfbal League]] | founded = {{Start date and years ago|1916|12|6 df=yes}} (as GOKC) | history = | arena = [[Blauw-Wit Hal]] | capacity = | location = [[Amsterdam]], [[Netherlands]] | colors = | president = [[Edgar Tijhuis]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.akcblauw-wit.nl/content/club-%20en%20ledeninformatie/bestuur-bestuur|title=Bestuur|last=|first=|date=|website=akcblauw-wit.nl|publisher=|access-date=2 April 2016}}</ref> | coach = [[Barry Schep]] | championships = | website = [http://www.akcblauw-wit.nl/] }}
'''AKC Blauw-Wit''' (Amsterdamse Korfbal Club Blauw-Wit) is a [[Dutch people|Dutch]] [[korfball|korfball club]] located in [[Amsterdam]], [[Netherlands]]. The club was founded on 6 December 1916 under the name of GOKC (Geheel Onthouders Korfbal Club)<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.akcblauw-wit.nl/public/upload/files/clubhistorieamsterdam.pdf|title=Clubhistorie Amsterdam|last=|first=|date=|website=akcblauw-wit.nl|publisher=|access-date=1 April 2016}}</ref> and they play their home games in the [[Blauw-Wit Hal]]. The team plays in white/blue horizontally striped shirts and black shorts / skirts.
==History==
Since the existence of the [[Korfbal League]] Blauw-Wit has been represented in the top division. Blauw-Wit reached the play-off stages 5 times in 2012, 2013, 2015, 2016 and 2017 but only in 2017 they reached to the final.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://topsport.amsterdam/?q=page&n=372|title=AKC Blauw-Wit is zeker van de Ziggo Dome!|last=|first=|date=|website=topsport.amsterdam|publisher=|access-date=2 April 2016}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.omroepwest.nl/nieuws/3094006/Korfbal-League-TOP-ten-val-gebracht-Fortuna-houdt-kleine-kans-op-play-offs|title=Korfbal League: TOP ten val gebracht, Fortuna houdt kleine kans op play-offs|last=|first=|date=20 March 2016|website=omroepwest.nl|publisher=|access-date=2 April 2016}}</ref> Blauw-Wit is the only club from the capital to play in the highest korfball division.
