'''Ahmed Kaïd Stadium''' is a [[Association football|football]] [[stadium]] in [[Tiaret]], [[Algeria]]. It has a capacity of 30,000,<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.fussballtempel.net/caf/listecaf.html|title=Football stadiums of the world – Stadium List Africa {{!}} Football stadiums of the world|website=www.fussballtempel.net|language=de-DE|access-date=2018-02-02}}</ref> and it is the home stadium of local football team [[JSM Tiaret]].

