The '''Croatian Cycling Federation''' or '''HBS''' ({{lang-hr|Hrvatski biciklistički savez}}) is the national [[sport governing body|governing body]] of [[bicycle racing|cycle racing]] in [[Croatia]].
The HBS is a member of the [[Union Cycliste Internationale|UCI]] and the [[Union Européenne de Cyclisme|UEC]].
